lead_paragraph: South Africa's Olympic swimming champion Chad le Clos remains undecided on the intensity of his Rio de Janeiro Games schedule ahead of a much-anticipated showdown with idol and rival Michael Phelps in Brazil.

headline.main: Le Clos Focused on Phelps, Rio Schedule Blurry
